                            <comment id="13597443" author="sershe" created="Fri, 8 Mar 2013 19:35:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Agreed, I was implying that if &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8036&quot; title=&quot;ProtobufUtil.multi behavior is inconsistent in case of errors&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-8036&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-8036&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; were to be rejected for some reason we&apos;d need to have RME-specific fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
